<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Ivana Trump was spotted enjoying a solo day out in New York yesterday, dining al fresco at an Italian restaurant before visiting a hair salon.</p>

<p>The Czech-born ex-wife of US President Donald Trump was seen sitting at Bar Italia on New York's upper east side before a kind gentleman chaperoned her to the hairdressers. </p>

<p>When she emerged businesswoman Ivana, 71, was escorted back home by a young woman.</p>

<p>Dressed all in black, the mother of Donald Trump Jr, Ivanka Trump and Eric Trump wore a disposable face mask as she traveled home from the salon.</p>

